  <description><![CDATA[<p>We are pleased to welcome this hotel to our Winter 2017/18 programme. With a reputation for great value in this world class ski resort and set in a convenient location just back from the main high street within a stone’s throw of the Gornergrat railway, nightlife and numerous restaurants Zermatt is justifiably famous for. Offering the convenience of bed and breakfast accommodation with the freedom to eat out in resort each evening and sample the local cuisine.</p>]]></description>
